videos.description: Tennessee freshman Josiah-Jordan James gets fouled while rising up for a jumper, but contorts in the air and gets his shot to drop.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Tennessee's James drains off-balance and-1 jumper) 2019/12/18

videos.headline: Tennessee's James drains off-balance and-1 jumper

videos.description: Cincinnati's Keith Williams muscles home his dunk over a Tennessee defender then stares him down before running back on defense.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Williams stares down Vols defender after slam) 2019/12/18

videos.headline: Williams stares down Vols defender after slam

videos.description: Jordan Fulkerson gets the ball in transition and throws down an and-1 slam in the final moments to seal Cincinnati's 78-66 win over No. 21 Tennessee.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Fulkerson's and-1 jam caps Cinci's win vs. Tennessee) 2019/12/18

videos.headline: Fulkerson's and-1 jam caps Cinci's win vs. Tennessee
